metadata.description:
This is my first NFT art piece.

This "girl" is a boy.

We have the right to be who we are, to wear what we want, when we want, where we want.

You don't have to care what other people say or how much they laugh at you.

You are free to be who you are.

You can be who you want to be.

Collector get 2894x4093 pixel JPG image.
